==Spanish==

===Verb===
'''seguir'''

# to [[follow]]
#: ''¡Sígueme!'' &ndash; “Follow me!”
# to [[continue]]; to [[go on]]
#: ''Este [[tío]] sigue hablando sin parar.'' &ndash; “This guy keeps talking nonstop.”
#: ''No puedo seguir así.'' &ndash; “I can’t go on like this.”

